high_descs: Turn left to go to the arm brown leather arm chair.
Pick up the CD on the left front corner.
Turn right to go to the front of the end table on the left side of the bed.
Place the CD inside the drawer on the left side and close the drawer.
Turn around and go past the bed and the arm chair to the brown wooden table.
Pick up the CD on the left from the table.
Turn around and go back to the black end table next to the bed.
Place the CD inside the drawer on the right of the first CD and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two CDs to the drawer in the end table.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the chair.
Take the CD from the chair.
Turn right, go forward to the bed, turn left, go forward to the night stand.
Put the CD in the left side of the drawer in the night stand.
Turn around, go forward to the desk.
Take the left CD from the desk.
Turn around, go forward to the night stand.
Put the CD in the night stand drawer to the right of the first CD.
anns.task_desc: Put two CDs in a night stand drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the chair in the corner.
Pick up the disk in the chair.

Open the drawer to the nightstand and put the disk inside.

Put the disk in the drawer of the nightstand.
